Detailed Description

This class represents the Search Dialog, which takes care of enabling the user to search and to display results in a readable manner.

void CSearchDlg::AddResult ( CSearchFile *  toadd  ) 

Adds the provided result to the right result-list.

void CSearchDlg::UpdateResult ( CSearchFile *  toupdate  ) 

Updates a changed result.

Parameters:
A pointer to the updated CSearchFile.

This function will update the source-count and color of the result, and if needed, it will also move the result so that the current sorting is maintained.
